    public class Token
extends org.apache.uima.jcas.tcas.Annotation
    Annotation on a token, which may have arguments if they are predicates; useful in transforming text into a "logical form", with affordances similar to the ones provided in Extended WordNet and the like. --- Source: Murdock Updated by JCasGen Sat Nov 29 22:03:38 EST 2014 XML source: /Users/leixiao/Desktop/project-team02/project-team02/src/main/resources/type/OAQATypes.xml
